Step 5 - Calculate degrees of freedom

Interpreting the Proportions chart - look at the "All combined" category - the more different the other 'book_type' categories look from this the more likely the Chi Square test will detect a difference. Within each 'genre' category the 'genre' values add up to 1 i.e. 100%. This is not the same way of displaying data as a clustered bar chart although the similarity can be confusing.
